rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0001
rows.name: Right, now we just have to head back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Thinking about passing through those creatures again
makes me shudder, though.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0003
rows.name: Before that, let's have a boxed lunch, meh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0004
rows.name: Tatsu made them for everyone, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Thinking everyone was hungry,
I came riding on that spinning machine just now, meh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Wh- What are you saying!
You shouldn't come here in your real body![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0010
rows.name:
It's okay, meh. If we just eat a little lunch
and head back, surely we won't be attacked, meh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0011
rows.name:
What's with that baseless confidence!
And how are you going to get back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0012
rows.name:
The chopper already went back!
You have no choice but to walk![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0013
rows.name:
All the way through the forest!
On foot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0015
rows.name:
Q-Quickly, we have to get the chopper
to turn back[ST:wide ]â€•[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06090100_MSG0017
rows.name: Did they gather here to eat this guy?[ST:wait ]
